OL,8,GOur political system is dominated by
OL,9,Gpowerful people and powerful
OL,10,Gcorporations. We work to expose
OL,11,Gwrongdoing by taking advantage of
OL,12,Gmassive amounts of open-source
OL,13,Ginformation and skilled people who
OL,14,Gcare about fighting back. We’ll talk
OL,15,Gabout the tools of the OSINT trade,
OL,16,Gfrom supply chain tracing and
OL,17,Gsatellite imagery analysis to
OL,18,Gautomated aircraft tracking and
OL,19,Gcountersurveillance. We’ll also talk
OL,20,Gthrough some partially redacted
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
